etes platform tailored for hybrid multicloud</h1><p class=p2>KubeSphere is a distributed operating system for cloud-native application management, using Kubernetes as its kernel. It provides a plug-and-play architecture, allowing third-party applications to be seamlessly integrated into its ecosystem.</p><a href=/docs/quick-start/minimal-kubesphere-on-k8s/ aria-label="Install on Kubernetes" target=_blank rel="noopener noreferrer"><button class='download-btn download-btn1 common-btn'>Install on Kubernetes</button></a>
